WHEREAS, the Cemetery Committee of the University
                       recommends the establishment of a Presidents’ Plot at the University
                       Cemetery;

WHEREAS, an increase of $5 million in short-term loans is
                       required to provide sufficient short-term financing for a similar term for
                       the John Paul Jones Arena Project in anticipation of pledged gift receipts;

WHEREAS, the Board has approved a policy to limit
                       variable-rate debt to no more than 40 percent of the University’s total debt
                       financing;

WHEREAS, the Macfarlane family donors have requested that
                       the University transfer the Macfarlane Family Fellowship funds held by the
                       University to the Macfarlane Family Darden Jefferson Fellowship Fund;

